  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Business Development Executive",
  "description": "<h2>The Role</h2><p>As a catalyst for new business, you will be responsible for hunting and developing new opportunities by leveraging your experience, expertise, and internal resources to engage prospective clients. You will act as a spokesperson for Info-Tech, confidently engaging with HR practitioners, business owners, and C-suite leaders across various industries. Your role will be instrumental in enabling local SMEs to digitalize HR functions, delivering transformational customer outcomes.</p><h2>About the Role</h2><ul><li>Develop and manage long-term strategic relationships with prospective and existing clients</li><li>Identify, manage, and close multiple opportunities and projects concurrently to drive commercial growth</li><li>Work towards monthly targets aligned with team goals</li><li>Provide pre-sales technical and functional support to prospective clients and customers, ensuring high customer satisfaction with minimal supervision</li><li>Participate actively in team meetings and contribute valuable insights and ideas</li><li>Maintain accurate visibility and forecasting of sales activities using CRM systems and relevant metrics</li><li>Target and influence new customers to adopt the full range of Info-Tech products</li></ul><h2>About You</h2><ul><li>Strong work ethic – self-motivated, driven, and hungry to succeed. You thrive on learning, growth, and achievement, whether in sales, sports, or other competitive pursuits</li><li>Keen interest in working within a fast-paced sales environment</li><li>Team player with excellent verbal and written communication skills</li><li>Proactive and confident in decision-making, embracing change as an opportunity</li><li>Strong project management skills with the ability to multitask and maintain operational effectiveness</li><li><strong>Prior experience in accounting software sales will be a strong advantage</strong></li><li><strong>Candidates with a finance or accounting background who are keen to transition into a business development or sales role are also encouraged to apply</strong></li></ul>",
