    "description": "<p>We help to make managing businesses easy by providing an All-in-one solution to manage human resource matters, and also, accounting works.<br>\n<br>\nOur Human Resource Management System(HRMS) provides a complete solution which includes real time facial recognition authentication, Cloud Mobile Attendance App, Time Attendance, Payroll, Leaves, Claims, Project Costing and Appraisal Software.<br>\n<br>\nThis goes hand in hand with our Accounting Software which manages another side of the business. You are able to manage accounting work like tracking, creating and sending bills, analysing profits, retrieving reports etc anywhere and anytime.</p>",
